These applications demonstrate usage and features of ilixi UI toolkit (http://www.ilixi.org).

Some applications might require installation of resource files into DATADIR.

This package contains the following applications:

  ilixi_hello_world	- Simplest application with a label.
  ilixi_gallery		- Demonstrates standard widgets.
  ilixi_mp		- Shows how to use videoplayer widget. (Not finished!)
  ilixi_monitor		- A simple resource monitor.

